reviews.review_text: Augusta '84 This show is why I loved touring ... one of the best shows in all of 84 tour ....

Augusta 1984 Front row for general admission.
Best Morning Dew ever! I defy you to find one better.
recommended An excellent recording of a smoking show. Must certainly be the best I have heard from '84. Especially Garcia seems really 'on' but the whole band is cooking,
